\n    \\\"path\\\": \\\"mise.toml\\\",\\n    \\\"line\\\": 26,\\n    \\\"comments\\\": [\\n      {\\n        \\\"author\\\": \\\"cursor[bot]\\\",\\n        \\\"body\\\": \\\"### Completions task deleted without creating replacement file\\\\n\\\\n**High Severity**\\\\n\\\\n<!-- DESCRIPTION START -->\\\\nThe `[tasks.\\\\\\\"completions\\\\\\\"]` block was removed from `mise.toml` but no corresponding `mise-tasks/completions` file was created, unlike every other migrated task. `.goreleaser.yaml` line 6 still calls `mise run completions` as a before-hook, so all goreleaser builds (including releases) will now fail with a \\\\\\\"task not found\\\\\\\" error.\\\\n<!-- DESCRIPTION END -->\\\\n\\\\n<!-- BUGBOT_BUG_ID: be7098e4-ac26-4b0d-96d2-98c5c7fda662 -->\\\\n\\\\n<!-- LOCATIONS START\\\\nmise.toml#L23-L26\\\\nLOCATIONS END -->\\\\n<p><a href=\\\\\\\"https://cursor.com/open?REDACTED\\\" target=\\\\\\\"_blank\\\\\\\" rel=\\\\\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\\\\\"><picture><source media=\\\\\\\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\\\\\\\" srcset=\\\\\\\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/fix-in-cursor-dark.png\\\\\\\"><source media=\\\\\\\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\\\\\\\" srcset=\\\\\\\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/fix-in-cursor-light.png\\\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\\\"Fix in Cursor\\\\\\\" width=\\\\\\\"115\\\\\\\" height=\\\\\\\"28\\\\\\\" src=\\\\\\\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/fix-in-cursor-dark.png\\\\\\\"></picture></a>&nbsp;<a href=\\\\\\\"https://cursor.com/agents?REDACTED\\\" target=\\\\\\\"_blank\\\\\\\" rel=\\\\\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\\\\\"><picture><source media=\\\\\\\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\\\\\\\" srcset=\\\\\\\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/fix-in-web-dark.png\\\\\\\"><source media=\\\\\\\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\\\\\\\" srcset=\\\\\\\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/fix-in-web-light.png\\\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\\\"Fix in Web\\\\\\\" width=\\\\\\\"99\\\\\\\" height=\\\\\\\"28\\\\\\\" src=\\\\\\\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/fix-in-web-dark.png\\\